<HEADLINE> Zimbabwean President Visits Egypt </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, January 3 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwean President Robert Mugabe
arrived here today on a three-day visit to Egypt.
</P>
<P>
During the visit, he will hold talks with his Egyptian
counterpart Hosni Mubarak on bilateral relations, current events
in the African continent, and the latest developments of the
