<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 4 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
January 5 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -10 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. -19 degrees C., max. -8 degrees C., clear, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. -10 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., clear, calm to
strong breeze.
