<DOCNO> XIE19980104.0095 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-01-04 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> New Way to Help Learn Chinese Quickly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 4 (Xinhua) -- Chinese experts have found a way
that can double the speed of learning Chinese characters.
</P>
<P>
The method will enable students to familiar with thousands of
Chinese characters within two or three years, compared to six
years when the conventional way is used, experts from Beijing
Languages and Culture University say.
</P>
<P>
Linguists have made new conclusions that the complicated
Chinese language system is based on only 500 basic
characters. Other characters are constructed with the 500 "bricks".
</P>
<P>
Therefore, the best way to learn Chinese is to learn the 500
characters, according to them.
</P>
<P>
The method is especially helpful for foreigners to learn
Chinese, which is becoming popular in some countries as more
students there want to link their future to China's economic
development, the experts note.
</P>
<P>
A Chinese-English book will soon be published by the Xinhua
Publishing House to explain the method, sources say. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19980104.0096 </DOCNO>
